{"tid":2442523,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「我想帶她回家」　311後老先生潛水470次尋妻","createTime":"2021-03-11T11:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:20:58.000Z","uid":75969,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3a83e2cf560339148e8e7953bf947e5fc8295cb2","tid":2442523,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"記者林辰彥／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n10年前的3月11日下午2時46分，日本東海岸遭9級強震襲擊，超過18000人的生命被吞噬。經過3654個日夜，如今福島核汙染問題仍讓世人關切，部分居民已經陸續回到家園，或者回去看看曾經的家。<br />\n<br />\n現年64歲的高松康雄原先是公車司機，大地震發生時，他收到妻子佑子傳給他8個字的簡訊，隨後音訊全無，高松康雄努力學習潛水3年，3年之後到現在的7年期間，高松康雄下海潛水數百次直到現在。<br />\n<br />\n當時在市中心銀行工作的佑子傳給他的簡訊「你沒事吧？我想回家」，之後市中心遭到海嘯毀滅性的摧毀，從此音訊全無。好友告訴高松康雄，當時所有銀行員工都上屋頂避難，後來全都被海嘯沖走。<br />\n<br />\n高松康雄後來踏遍所有避難所與停屍間，都沒找到佑子的下落，2011年11月高松康雄為佑子舉行葬哩，埋的是佑子的眼鏡以及在銀行遺址附近發現的手機。<br />\n<br />\n當時高松康雄把佑子的手機拿去維修，發現佑子沒來得及發送出去的簡訊寫著「海嘯太厲害了！」「已經逼近到腳下了。」<br />\n<br />\n高松康雄取得潛水國家級執照後，他每個星期都會下海潛水一、兩個小時，每次都會下潛到40多公尺深度，在光線無法透射到的地方仔細尋找。他已經累計潛水了470次以上。<br />\n<br />\n高松康雄知道這個希望極其渺茫，但是高松康雄收到妻子最後訊息是「我想回家」，高松康雄說：「我想帶她回家！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=909069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D909069&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=024085b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D909069&h=60fe694a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=909069</a>"},{"pid":"e917a973f40703e3c5769f4ae6ec633e08748cb7","tid":2442523,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fcecc649853f38de40538b68903957cb1a0eb9","tid":2442523,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"算啦, 襯仲有氣有力 搵過第個老婆好過"},{"pid":"404e5de5c448859516e1d9f1eaa6bd5755badb18","tid":2442523,"uid":129739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"salute"},{"pid":"4bf8ca2506275640cebe35a7e84c2d636f305494","tid":2442523,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"唉....."},{"pid":"70c9c0aa9ac85ac7dca15db7876c5f814e339bc9","tid":2442523,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"日本人咁高質，係天災逼出黎"},{"pid":"09da641efcad597d02fb246e4378b3fb2eeb0572","tid":2442523,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee08836f31ec4dd510cff29ca304aede144fdf0","tid":2442523,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91cbb910fe533d5727c5e0b79dc59884c92d4da","tid":2442523,"uid":132189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914ae7957ef39dda33d042278547f037c42d7688","tid":2442523,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:17:31.000Z","msg":"真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d793d527bd1c3da8ee27c3d9b8a7d60be929ed6","tid":2442523,"uid":263391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a98f10b8138ba1a347343b2d992a62e9c44ab76","tid":2442523,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"73fcecc649853f38